
CET6listening 
rules
1.视听一致：适合四六级听力所有题型，
           边听边选，不等问题，
           选被击中最多词语为准确答案。
  选项核心位置：
          动宾/系表结构，即 否定词 动词 名词 形容词（尤其是最高级比较级）
                           否动名形
  先把题作对，再把题听懂，
  写在前面，听力是不可能听懂的，只可能听懂局部词。
  划动宾/系表，重点听词。一般划2个，最多3个。一个句子由3个块组成，动作发起者+动/系+宾/表。
  典型例题：
      1.A)He would feel *insulted  v+adj 动作发起者完全相同，就不要看前面的了，动词几乎一样，只看后面的adj，如加*的词
        B)He would feel very *sad
        C)He would be *embarrassed
        D)He would be *disappointed
      2.A)They are eager to become famous    v+adj 动作发起者差不多，这里很多词都是不一样的，勾划否动名形，如eager，famous 
        B)Many lack professional training                                                               lack，training
        C)Few will become successful                                                                    become，successful 
        D)They live a glamorous life                                                                    live， glamorous      
      3.A)Red-haired women were regarded as more reliable   v+adj    regarded,  reliable          因为前面动作发起者很不一样，所以前面的颜色可以划一下，Red
        B)Brown-haired women were rated as more capable               rated, capable                                                               Brown
        C)Golden-haired women were considered attractive              considered, attractive                                                       Golden
        D)Black-haired women were judged to be intelligent             judged, intelligent                                                         Black
      4.A)They are *smart and *eloquent     v+adj  动作发起者完全相同，就不要看前面的了，动词几乎一样，只看后面的adj，如加*的词
        B)They are *ambitious and *arrogant
        C)They are *shrewd and *dishonest
        D)They are *wealthy and *industrious
      5.A)The urgency of pension reform     纯名词，就找纯名词部分，  pension reform        一般不会是一个词，最少两个词，用技巧，连续被读到的选项更容易是错的，完整被读到，单独被读到容易正确
        B)Medical care for senior citizens                          medical care              这道题在更多情况下，就是一个把ABD排除后的结果
        C)Finding meaningful roles for the elderly in society       finding meaning roles
        D)The development of public facilities for senior citizens  development of public facilities
      6.A)Government's role in resolving an economic crisis         纯名词，resolving economic crisis      adj不要管，专划名词，选被击中最多的，选项。
        B)The worsening real wage situation around the world               real wage situation
        C)Indications of economic recovery in the United States             economic recovery
        D)The impact of the current economic crisis on people's life        current economic crisis
2. 同义替换：
        注意一切词性替换及含义替换
        是能力，不是技巧
        每一题，都要总结(学习选项和原文的对应)
      7.A)
        B)
        C)
        D)
      8.A)
        B)
        C)
        D)
      9.A)
        B)
        C)
        D)
           

